race.comment: SHE'S A COWGIRL (1) was in a rearwards position on the turn last time out before finishing 17 lengths from the winner in eighth over 1106m at this track (Dirt). This looks a nice race so expect her to be right in the finish. JAUNTY (9) was out of the money on debut two runs back then again missed the frame last start when she was never in contention over 1006m at this track, beaten 15 lengths into seventh. Will enjoy a drop in class so she is sure to be prominent. CINCALITA (3) has not raced since her debut back on July 13 when she finished sixth over 1509m at Lone Star Park (Turf). Top-three chance with that run under her belt. MO'O LIO (8) finished out of the money on debut two starts back then she got a long way back and was beaten 16 lengths when sixth in a 1207m contest at this track four weeks ago. Finds a nice race and can get the job done. Something for the Multiples: QUIXX (6)
